                    6661   ; *                            OS_ERR_PEND_ISR     If you called this function from an ISR and the result
                    6662   ; *                                                would lead to a suspension.
                    6663   ; *                            OS_ERR_PEVENT_NULL  If 'pevent' is a NULL pointer
                    6664   ; *                            OS_ERR_PEND_LOCKED  If you called this function when the scheduler is locked
