                    6858   ; *                                     ABORT WAITING ON A MESSAGE MAILBOX
                    6859   ; *
                    6860   ; * Description: This function aborts & readies any tasks currently waiting on a mailbox.  This function
                    6861   ; *              should be used to fault-abort the wait on the mailbox, rather than to normally signal
                    6862   ; *              the mailbox via OSMboxPost() or OSMboxPostOpt().
                    6863   ; *
