                    6865   ; *
                    6866   ; *              opt           determines the type of ABORT performed:
                    6867   ; *                            OS_PEND_OPT_NONE         ABORT wait for a single task (HPT) waiting on the
                    6868   ; *                                                     mailbox
                    6869   ; *                            OS_PEND_OPT_BROADCAST    ABORT wait for ALL tasks that are  waiting on the
                    6870   ; *                                                     mailbox
                    6871   ; *
                    6872   ; *              perr          is a pointer to where an error message will be deposited.  Possible error
                    6873   ; *                            messages are:
                    6874   ; *
                    6875   ; *                            OS_ERR_NONE         No tasks were     waiting on the mailbox.
                    6876   ; *                            OS_ERR_PEND_ABORT   At least one task waiting on the mailbox was readied
                    6877   ; *                                                and informed of the aborted wait; check return value
                    6878   ; *                                                for the number of tasks whose wait on the mailbox
                    6879   ; *                                                was aborted.
                    6880   ; *                            OS_ERR_EVENT_TYPE   If you didn't pass a pointer to a mailbox.
                    6881   ; *                            OS_ERR_PEVENT_NULL  If 'pevent' is a NULL pointer.
                    6882   ; *
                    6883   ; * Returns    : == 0          if no tasks were waiting on the mailbox, or upon error.
                    6884   ; *              >  0          if one or more tasks waiting on the mailbox are now readied and informed.
                    6885   ; *********************************************************************************************************
                    6886   ; */
