                    11791   ; /*
                    11792   ; *********************************************************************************************************
                    11793   ; *                                    ABORT WAITING ON A SEMAPHORE
                    11794   ; *
                    11795   ; * Description: This function aborts & readies any tasks currently waiting on a semaphore.  This function
                    11796   ; *              should be used to fault-abort the wait on the semaphore, rather than to normally signal
                    11797   ; *              the semaphore via OSSemPost().
