                    11800   ; *                            semaphore.
                    11801   ; *
                    11802   ; *              opt           determines the type of ABORT performed:
                    11803   ; *                            OS_PEND_OPT_NONE         ABORT wait for a single task (HPT) waiting on the
                    11804   ; *                                                     semaphore
                    11805   ; *                            OS_PEND_OPT_BROADCAST    ABORT wait for ALL tasks that are  waiting on the
                    11806   ; *                                                     semaphore
                    11807   ; *
                    11808   ; *              perr          is a pointer to where an error message will be deposited.  Possible error
                    11809   ; *                            messages are:
                    11810   ; *
                    11811   ; *                            OS_ERR_NONE         No tasks were     waiting on the semaphore.
                    11812   ; *                            OS_ERR_PEND_ABORT   At least one task waiting on the semaphore was readied
                    11813   ; *                                                and informed of the aborted wait; check return value
                    11814   ; *                                                for the number of tasks whose wait on the semaphore
                    11815   ; *                                                was aborted.
                    11816   ; *                            OS_ERR_EVENT_TYPE   If you didn't pass a pointer to a semaphore.
                    11817   ; *                            OS_ERR_PEVENT_NULL  If 'pevent' is a NULL pointer.
                    11818   ; *
                    11819   ; * Returns    : == 0          if no tasks were waiting on the semaphore, or upon error.
                    11820   ; *              >  0          if one or more tasks waiting on the semaphore are now readied and informed.
                    11821   ; *********************************************************************************************************
                    11822   ; */
